      <title>欧盟寻求印度对俄罗斯制裁的帮助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/eu-to-seek-india-s-help-to-enforce-sanctions-on-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟委员会主席厄休拉·冯·莱恩（Ursula von der Leyen）将要求印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪（Narendra Modi）的协助，以实施对俄罗斯的制裁，当时两位领导人本周在新德里开会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/eu-to-seek-india-s-help-to-enforce-sanctions-on-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 15:35:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bessent说，Doge的努力与“政府淘汰”无关</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/bessent-says-doge-effort-isn-t-about-government-elimination</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent）继续对托管联邦劳动力和遏制公共支出的努力的努力不断震惊，称其名称并不代表“政府部门淘汰”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/bessent-says-doge-effort-isn-t-about-government-elimination</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 15:20:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>餐馆警告潜在的120亿美元受到特朗普关税的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/restaurants-warn-of-potential-12-billion-hit-from-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代表餐馆的美国贸易集团敦促唐纳德·特朗普总统免除饮料免税，估计税款可能使该行业损失超过120亿美元，并导致消费者的价格更高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/restaurants-warn-of-potential-12-billion-hit-from-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 15:18:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对于美元，“玛格拉戈协定”将意味着什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/will-trump-devalue-the-us-dollar-with-a-mar-a-lago-accord</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的积极计划，以改变美国与世界其他地区的交易方式，激发了人们对大型跨国公款的潜力，这些跨国公司将故意削弱美元;帮助美国出口商与中国和日本等竞争对手竞争。在佛罗里达州棕榈滩的特朗普私人俱乐部之后，分析师已经定居在名字“ Mar-a-Lago Accord”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/will-trump-devalue-the-us-dollar-with-a-mar-a-lago-accord</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 14:50:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁Feinberg说，五角大楼需要投资者精明的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/billionaire-feinberg-says-he-ll-bring-investor-savvy-to-pentagon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统在五角大楼排名第二的亿万富翁史蒂夫·费恩伯格（Steve Feinberg）表示，他的私募股权投资背景使他成为解决那里长期招待问题的理想候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/billionaire-feinberg-says-he-ll-bring-investor-savvy-to-pentagon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 14:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西金融负责人说，卢拉命令他修理预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/brazil-finance-chief-says-lula-gave-him-mission-to-fix-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西财务负责人说，他已经收到了直接从路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达·席尔瓦（Luiz Inacio Lula da Silva）总统的公共帐户平衡的使命，许多投资者认为，他不愿意削减目标的痛苦支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/brazil-finance-chief-says-lula-gave-him-mission-to-fix-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 13:12:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国的社会民主党人向2000亿欧元开放国防基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/social-democrats-open-to-200-billion-for-german-defense-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国的社会民主党人表示，他们愿意通过放宽规则限制政府借贷或创建另一个特殊基金来筹集大幅增加军事支出的想法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/social-democrats-open-to-200-billion-for-german-defense-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 13:05:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Milei效应：百万美元合同诱使阿根廷足球明星回家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/milei-s-strong-peso-revives-argentine-soccer-with-million-dollar-contracts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几十年来，阿根廷陷入了一系列永无止境的经济危机中，一直在出口其顶级足球运动员。就像当地的粉丝群一样热情，这里的团队根本没有足够的财务能力与顶级外国俱乐部悬挂的合同竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/milei-s-strong-peso-revives-argentine-soccer-with-million-dollar-contracts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国试图将国防预算提高到俄罗斯担心的3％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/uk-defense-budget-to-hit-3-of-gdp-in-next-decade-starmer-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）概述了英国国防支出及其巨大增加的计划；在未来十年中，上升到经济产出的3％;随着欧洲政府寻求加强其安全性，因为对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）领导下的美国支持的怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/uk-defense-budget-to-hit-3-of-gdp-in-next-decade-starmer-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 12:49:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非的DA拒绝新税，呼吁削减支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/south-africa-s-da-rejects-new-taxes-calls-for-expenditure-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党联盟是南非的第二大政党，也是该国统治联盟的成员，拒绝征收任何新税收，并呼吁进行削减和改革以加速经济增长以帮助稳定国家预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/south-africa-s-da-rejects-new-taxes-calls-for-expenditure-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 10:27:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
